sql:
SELECT COUNT(file_id) 
FROM file_uploads 
WHERE user_id = (SELECT user_id FROM users WHERE email = 'john.doe@example.com');

external_knowledge:
- File names are assumed to be unique identifiers for each file in the database;
- Product names are the actual names of the products that the files are associated with;
- Users are identified by their unique user IDs, but the query returns their full names for clarity.
